      <ab type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Young Emir Kusturica, with short hair and without a beard, in front of a building.</ab>
      <ab subtype="comment" type="lido:objectDescriptionSet">Kusturica is a filmmaker, actor and musician (with the band ‘The No Smoking Orchestra’). He has twice won the Palme d’Or at Cannes: for ‘Otac na službenom putu’ (When father was away on business, 1985), and for ‘Podzemlje’ (Underground, 1995). He is a colourful and controversial character and was baptized into the Serbian Orthodox Church in 2005.</ab>
